          order: 2,
          content: "# CSS Colors, Text & Fonts\n\nColors, text, and fonts are fundamental to web design. They establish the visual hierarchy and mood of your website.\n\n## CSS Colors\n\n### Color Values\n\n### 1. Color Names\nPredefined color names:\n```css\nh1 {\n  color: red;\n  background-color: lightblue;\n}\n```\n\n### 2. HEX Colors\nHexadecimal color notation:\n```css\nh1 {\n  color: #ff0000; /* Red */\n  background-color: #0000ff; /* Blue */\n}\n```\n\n### 3. RGB Colors\nRGB (Red, Green, Blue) values:\n```css\nh1 {\n  color: rgb(255, 0, 0); /* Red */\n  background-color: rgb(0, 0, 255); /* Blue */\n}\n```\n\n### 4. RGBA Colors\nRGB with Alpha (transparency):\n```css\nh1 {\n  color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Semi-transparent red */\n  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.3); /* Semi-transparent blue */\n}\n```\n\n### 5. HSL Colors\nHue, Saturation, Lightness:\n```css\nh1 {\n  color: hsl(0, 100%, 50%); /* Red */\n  background-color: hsl(240, 100%, 50%); /* Blue */\n}\n```\n\n### 6. HSLA Colors\nHSL with Alpha (transparency):\n```css\nh1 {\n  color: hsla(0, 100%, 50%, 0.5); /* Semi-transparent red */\n}\n```\n\n## CSS Text Properties\n\n### Text Color\n```css\nbody {\n  color: #333333; /* Dark gray text */\n}\n```\n\n### Text Alignment\n```css\nh1 {\n  text-align: center; /* left, center, right, justify */\n}\n\np {\n  text-align: justify;\n}\n```\n\n### Text Decoration\n```css\na {\n  text-decoration: none; /* none, underline, overline, line-through */\n}\n\nh1 {\n  text-decoration: underline;\n}\n\n.strikethrough {\n  text-decoration: line-through;\n}\n```\n\n### Text Transformation\n```css\n.uppercase {\n  text-transform: uppercase; /* uppercase, lowercase, capitalize, none */\n}\n\n.lowercase {\n  text-transform: lowercase;\n}\n\n.capitalize {\n  text-transform: capitalize;\n}\n```\n\n### Text Indentation\n```css\np {\n  text-indent: 50px; /* Indents first line of text */\n}\n```\n\n### Letter Spacing\n```css\nh1 {\n  letter-spacing: 3px; /* Increase space between letters */\n}\n\n.tight {\n  letter-spacing: -1px; /* Decrease space between letters */\n}\n```\n\n### Line Height\n```css\np {\n  line-height: 1.6; /* 1.6 times the font size */\n}\n\np.tight {\n  line-height: 1.2;\n}\n\np.loose {\n  line-height: 2.0;\n}\n```\n\n### Text Shadow\n```css\nh1 {\n  text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000000;\n  /* x-offset y-offset blur color */\n}\n```\n\n## CSS Fonts\n\n### Font Family\n\n#### Generic Font Families\n- `serif` - Characters with serifs (small lines at the ends)\n- `sans-serif` - Characters without serifs\n- `monospace` - All characters have the same width\n- `cursive` - Handwritten style fonts\n- `fantasy` - Decorative fonts\n\n```css\nbody {\n  font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;\n}\n\nh1 {\n  font-family: \"Times New Roman\", Times, serif;\n}\n\ncode {\n  font-family: \"Courier New\", Courier, monospace;\n}\n```\n\n### Font Style\n```css\np.normal {\n  font-style: normal; /* normal, italic, oblique */\n}\n\np.italic {\n  font-style: italic;\n}\n```\n\n### Font Size\n\n#### Using Pixels\n```css\nh1 {\n  font-size: 40px;\n}\n\np {\n  font-size: 16px;\n}\n```\n\n#### Using Em (relative to parent font size)\n```css\nh1 {\n  font-size: 2.5em; /* 2.5 times the parent font size */\n}\n\np {\n  font-size: 1em; /* Same as parent font size */\n}\n```\n\n#### Using Rem (relative to root font size)\n```css\nh1 {\n  font-size: 2.5rem; /* 2.5 times the root font size */\n}\n```\n\n#### Using Viewport Width (responsive)\n```css\nh1 {\n  font-size: 5vw; /* 5% of viewport width */\n}\n```\n\n#### Using Percentage\n```css\nh1 {\n  font-size: 200%;\n}\n```\n\n### Font Weight\n```css\np.normal {\n  font-weight: normal; /* 400 */\n}\n\np.light {\n  font-weight: lighter; /* 100 */\n}\n\np.thick {\n  font-weight: bold; /* 700 */\n}\n\np.thicker {\n  font-weight: 900;\n}\n```",
          codeSnippet: "/* Typography Practice */\nbody {\n  font-family: 'Helvetica', Arial, sans-serif;\n  color: #333333;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n}\n\nh1, h2, h3 {\n  color: #2c3e50;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n}\n\nh1 {\n  font-size: 2.5rem;\n  text-align: center;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  letter-spacing: 2px;\n}\n\nh2 {\n  font-size: 2rem;\n  margin-bottom: 0.8em;\n}\n\np {\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  margin-bottom: 1em;\n  text-align: justify;\n}\n\n.highlight {\n  color: #e74c3c;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  background-color: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.1);\n  padding: 2px 4px;\n  border-radius: 3px;\n}\n\n.link {\n  color: #3498db;\n  text-decoration: none;\n  font-style: italic;\n}\n\n.link:hover {\n  text-decoration: underline;\n  color: #2980b9;\n}\n\ncode {\n  font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;\n  background-color: #f4f4f4;\n  padding: 2px 6px;\n  border-radius: 3px;\n  font-size: 0.9em;\n}",
